    "title": "Business Post India is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Senior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Business Post India! We are hiring a Warehouse Manager for our Vadodara team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Business Post India:\nBusiness Post India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Business Post India!",
